code: export function getGrid(width,height){var grid=[];for(var i=0;i<height;i++){var local=[];for(var j=0;j<width;j++){local.push({x:j,y:i,isstart:false,istarget:false,weight:1,iswall:false});}grid.push(local);}grid[Math.floor(height/2)][Math.floor(width/2)].isstart=true;grid[height-2][width-2].istarget=true;return grid;}
